uot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;We recommend you take note of this unsubscription during your next interactions with &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://carmignac-crm--uatmycrm.sandbox.lightning.force.com/builder_platform_interaction/%7B!RecordURL%7D&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;{!$Record.FirstName} {!$Record.LastName}&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;, to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;ensure that our communication remains aligned with their preferences&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;Best regards,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12px; font-family: &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;Salesforce Support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
